<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
<title>每周大转盘</title>
<script src="https://telegram.org/js/telegram-web-app.js"></script>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#140915;
  --bg2:#261325;
  --line:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  --text:#f8fafc;
  --muted:#b5bfd3;
  --gold:#f59e0b;
  --rose:#fb7185;
  --cyan:#22d3ee;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
body{
  min-height:100vh;
  font-family:"SF Pro Display","Noto Sans SC","PingFang SC",system-ui,sans-serif;
  color:var(--text);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(245,158,11,.22), transparent 28%),
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(251,113,133,.18), transparent 26%),
    linear-gradient(165deg, var(--bg), var(--bg2));
}
.shell{min-height:100vh;padding:16px;display:flex;justify-content:center}
.board{
  width:min(100%,430px);
  border-radius:30px;
  overflow:hidden;
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.08), rgba(255,255,255,.03));
  box-shadow:0 28px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  backdrop-filter:blur(18px);
}
.hero{padding:16px 16px 10px}
.eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ffe7bb}
.dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),#fde68a);box-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(245,158,11,.8)}
.title{margin-top:12px;font-size:30px;font-weight:900}
.subtitle{margin-top:6px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--muted)}
.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;margin-top:14px}
.stat{padding:10px 8px;border-radius:16px;text-align:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.stat-k{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}
.stat-v{margin-top:4px;font-size:18px;font-weight:800}
.panel{margin:0 16px 12px;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
.panel-k{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}
.panel-v{margin-top:6px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5}
.wheel-wrap{position:relative;margin:8px 16px 14px;padding:18px;border-radius:28px;background:radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255,255,255,.08), rgba(255,255,255,.02));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.pointer{
  position:absolute;left:50%;top:8px;transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:0;height:0;border-left:15px solid transparent;border-right:15px solid transparent;border-top:28px solid #fff3d0;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.25));z-index:3;
}
.wheel-ring{
  position:relative;margin:0 auto;width:min(70vw,288px);height:min(70vw,288px);max-width:288px;max-height:288px;
  border-radius:50%;
  padding:12px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.18), rgba(255,255,255,.04));
  box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.08), 0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
}
.wheel{
  position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:50%;
  background:
    conic-gradient(
      #f59e0b 0deg 45deg,
      #fb7185 45deg 90deg,
      #22d3ee 90deg 135deg,
      #8b5cf6 135deg 180deg,
      #10b981 180deg 225deg,
      #f97316 225deg 270deg,
      #0ea5e9 270deg 315deg,
      #ec4899 315deg 360deg
    );
  border:8px solid rgba(16,12,24,.82);
  transition:transform 4.6s cubic-bezier(.12,.88,.14,1);
  overflow:hidden;
}
.wheel::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;inset:50%;width:60px;height:60px;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fff8de, #f59e0b);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(17,12,27,.86);
}
.segment-label{
  position:absolute;left:50%;top:50%;
  width:64px;
  transform-origin:0 0;
  font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0;color:#fff;text-align:center;
  text-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
}
.cta{padding:0 16px 16px}
.spin-btn{
  width:100%;border:0;border-radius:18px;padding:16px 18px;
  font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, #fb7185, #f59e0b);
  box-shadow:0 16px 32px rgba(245,158,11,.22);
}
.spin-btn:disabled{opacity:.5;box-shadow:none}
.result{margin:0 16px 16px;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:20px;background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.08), rgba(255,255,255,.03));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.result-tag{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#e8d5ff}
.result-title{margin-top:8px;font-size:22px;font-weight:900}
.result-sub{margin-top:4px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;min-height:20px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="shell">
  <div class="board">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Weekly Lucky Wheel</div>
      <div class="title">每周大转盘</div>
      <div class="subtitle">每周只有 1 次机会。指针停下的那一格，就是这周的流量奖励。</div>
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-k">每周次数</div><div class="stat-v">1</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-k">最高奖励</div><div class="stat-v">50GB</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-k">最低奖励</div><div class="stat-v">5GB</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-k">本周状态</div>
      <div class="panel-v" id="status-text">正在读取本周转盘状态...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="wheel-wrap">
      <div class="pointer"></div>
      <div class="wheel-ring">
        <div class="wheel" id="wheel">
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(-67.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">50GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(-22.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">30GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(22.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">20GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(67.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">15GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(112.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">10GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(157.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">8GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(202.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">5GB</div>
          <div class="segment-label" style="transform:rotate(247.5deg) translate(-32px,-116px);">5GB</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta">
      <button type="button" class="spin-btn" id="spin-btn">开始转盘</button>
    </div>
    <div class="result">
      <div class="result-tag">Spin Result</div>
      <div class="result-title" id="result-title">指针还没转动</div>
      <div class="result-sub" id="result-sub">本周抽中后会立即到账，下周一再开启新一轮。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script src="/js/lucky-wheel.js?v=<%= assetVersion %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
